        - The distance to the left wall is: [0.8, 0.7, 0.9, 0.6, 0.8, 0.7, 0.9, 0.6, 0.8, 0.7, 0.9]


        - The distance to the right wall is: [0.7, 0.8, 0.6, 0.9, 0.7, 0.8, 0.6, 0.9, 0.7, 0.8, 0.6]

 
        - Bool if the car is reversing: False

          
        - Bool if the car has crashed: False

        
        - Bool if the car is facing the wall: False


   
        Use these guides to reason: 

Hint 11:
Unless told otherwise, you should be driving forwards!
Hint 6:

        Check if the car is adhering to what the human wants: Don't move. Strictly reply in the following format: 

        Adhering to Human: <True/False>
